Module org.eclipse.persistence.core
Package org.eclipse.persistence.descriptors.partitioning

Class RangePartition

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.persistence.descriptors.partitioning.RangePartition
public class RangePartition extends Object
PUBLIC: Represent a specific range partition. Values >= startValue and <= endValue will be routed to the connection pool.
Since:
EclipseLink 2.2
